data.description: Welcome to 3975 Madison Ave. This rare and beautiful Shadyside property offers many country-like features while conveniently located right on the edge of town. Enjoy breathtaking views of the town and river while you enjoy your morning coffee on the porch. The just over an acre of land ensures a sense of privacy, making the outdoor space that features a large deck, hot tub, and fire pit the perfect setting for relaxing, fun family nights, or entertaining. This spacious home features four bedrooms, including a luxurious master suite with laundry on the main floor, providing both privacy and convenience. The sizable and timeless eat-in kitchen offers plenty of beautiful cabinetry, countertop space, and modern appliances ideal for those that love to cook. The living room offers the perfect balance of feeling cozy while remaining grand, fit for a movie night or entertaining during the holidays. Your guests will also have the convenience of a half bath on the main floor. Upstairs, you will find a full bathroom that serves two very generously sized bedrooms with unlimited potential of use. Step downstairs, and you'll find a thoughtfully designed in-law suite in the finished basement – complete with an open concept kitchen and living area, laundry, bedroom, bonus room, and full bathroom. This space is perfect for spreading out, guests or extended family, providing both independence and comfort. Here, you will also find a work space as well as extensive storage space. The 2-car attached garage adds practicality to daily life, offering shelter for your cars, extra storage space and easy access to the kitchen. The graveled area offers plenty of parking, accommodating for a large family or guests. This stunning Shadyside property has so much to offer, including a one year home warranty! Schedule your showing to appreciate the beauty of this home in person!
